# Music Video Generator

This project creates a Flask-based web application that generates music videos based on uploaded audio files and optional images. It uses various tools for audio analysis, waveform visualization, and video creation.

## Features

- Upload audio files (.mp3, .wav, .m4a)
- Optionally upload images for custom visuals
- Apply different themes to the generated video
- Generate high-quality music videos with waveform visualizations
- Download the generated video

## Installation

To run this project locally:

1. Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/njg37/music_video_generator.git


2. Install Python dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt


3. Set up a virtual environment:
python -m venv venv source venv/bin/activate # On Windows, use venv\Scripts\activate


4. Run the Flask application:
python app.py


## Usage

1. Open a web browser and navigate to `http://localhost:5000`.
2. Select an audio file to upload.
3. Optionally select an image file for custom visuals.
4. Choose a theme for the video.
5. Click "Upload" to start the video generation process.
6. Once complete, download your generated music video.

## Technologies Used

- Flask: Web framework
- Werkzeug: File handling utilities
- OpenCV: Image processing
- MoviePy: Video editing
- Pydub: Audio manipulation
- Matplotlib: Waveform visualization

